OL,3,CChief Constable retires amid
OL,4,Cinvestigation into alleged gross
OL,5,Cmisconduct
OL,7,FThe Chief Constable of Hampshire and
OL,8,FIsle of Wight Constabulary has
OL,9,Fannounced his retirement, while being
OL,10,Finvestigated for potential gross
OL,11,Fmisconduct.
OL,13,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,14,FConduct (IOPC) is looking into
OL,15,Fallegations that Scott Chilton failed
OL,16,Fto disclose a conflict of interest
OL,17,Frelating to a previous relationship.
OL,19,FMr Chilton joined the force in 1992.
