OL,3,CChief Constable retires amid
OL,4,Cinvestigation into alleged gross
OL,5,Cmisconduct
OL,7,FIOPC director Derrick Campbell said:
OL,8,F"This morning, we notified the
OL,9,FHampshire and Isle of Wight
OL,10,FConstabulary's Chief Constable, Scott
OL,11,FChilton, that he is under
OL,12,Finvestigation for potential gross
OL,13,Fmisconduct.
OL,15,F"This follows indications that he may
OL,16,Fhave potentially breached police
OL,17,Fstandards of professional behaviour
OL,18,Frelating to honesty and integrity;
OL,19,Fduties and responsibilities;
OL,20,Fdiscreditable conduct; and orders and
OL,21,Finstructions.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
