OL,3,CChief Constable retires amid
OL,4,Cinvestigation into alleged gross
OL,5,Cmisconduct
OL,7,F"Our investigation, which involves
OL,8,Fallegations that he failed to disclose
OL,9,Fa conflict of interest relating to a
OL,10,Fworkplace relationship before he was
OL,11,Fchief constable, began following a
OL,12,Fconduct referral from the Hampshire
OL,13,Fand Isle of Wight Police and Crime
OL,14,FCommissioner (PCC) on 27 February.
