OL,3,CChief Constable retires amid
OL,4,Cinvestigation into alleged gross
OL,5,Cmisconduct
OL,7,F"It was widened to include a further
OL,8,Fallegation, involving failing to
OL,9,Fdisclose a conflict of interest
OL,10,Frelating to a further workplace
OL,11,Frelationship after becoming chief
OL,12,Fconstable, following a second conduct
OL,13,Freferral from the PCC's office on 31
OL,14,FMarch.
OL,16,F"We understand that the Chief
OL,17,FConstable has today retired from the
OL,18,Fforce with immediate effect. This will
OL,19,Fnot impact our investigation, which
OL,20,Fremains ongoing.
